  <title>JOGAR DISPUTAR BRINCAR!</title>

<section id="play">
<title>Como jogar</title>

<list>
  <item><p>The <key>←</key> and <key>→</key> keys move the blocks across the screen.</p></item>
  <item><p>The <key>↑</key> key rotates the block. The rotation (which is counterclockwise by default) can be changed in the <link xref="preferences">Preferences</link>.</p></item>
  <item><p>The <key>SPACEBAR</key> and <key>↓</key> key increase the speed of the drop. The <key>SPACEBAR</key> causes a hard-drop (instant move to the bottom). The <key>↓</key> key causes a soft-drop (temporary increase in speed while the key is held down).</p></item>
</list>
</section>

<section id="rules">
<title>Regras</title>

<p>There are a couple of rules that you should keep in mind:</p>
<list>
  <item><p>You can pause, end, start a new game, get help or quit the program at any time.</p></item>
  <item><p>Você pode pausar o jogo quantas vezes desejar.</p></item>
</list>
</section>

